steps.name: I skip linking my card
I click on "ACCOUNT" button
I check that the "Account Screen" is displayed
I click on "WALLET" tab
I check that the "Wallet Screen" is displayed
I wait for the "CREDIT CARD" list to have more or equal than 1 elements
I check the number of "CREDIT CARDS" added
I check that the actual value: "1" is greater or equal than value "1"
I click on "ADD PAYMENT" button
I accept Terms & Conditions
I check that the "Add Payment Method Pane" is displayed
I click on "PAYMENT CARD" button
I add credit card information
I check that the "Card successfully added" toast message is displayed
I wait for the "CREDIT CARD" list to have more or equal than 2 elements
I check the number of "CREDIT CARDS" added
I check that the actual value: "2" is greater than value "1"
I click on recently added ****4444 "CREDIT CARD THREE DOTS" button
I click on "SET AS DEFAULT" button
I check that the "Card successfully updated" toast message is displayed
I get the text from the default card number
I check that the application text: "****4444" is equals to expected value: "****4444"
